snippet.title: Kathryn Hahn on Her WandaVision Spin-off and Why She Avoids Social Media
snippet.description:
Kathryn Hahn sits down with Drew to discuss her incredible role in Marvel's WandaVision, why she decided to not use social media, and attempts to avoid spoilers as she tries to answer Drew's WandaVision spin-off questions!

#DrewBarrymoreShow #KathrynHahn #MCU
